abstract: "Production-tested Claude Code patterns reorganized into 6 topical Parts (Foundation, Workflow, Extension, Context Engineering, Advanced, Reference). Three install tiers: Core (8 rules, 3 skills, 1 hook), Recommended (30/16/7), Full (64/44/12 + 4 governance scripts). CC 2.1.111+ compatible."
